poetry run holmes ask --no-echo-request "lookup event $1 and summarize what happened + if you can fetch any information about the user from an employee information database please do so + fetch any other suspicious activities this user did. Finally, suggest a few theories about what happened here. ignore GetCallerIdentity as that can be called automatically by the aws cli and doesn't indicate anything. give concise output like '**XYZ event for <important details> performed by <user>**.\n\n**Analysis:** This event was/was not flagged as highly suspicuous because...\n\n**Recommendations:** ...\n\n.' Make sure to cite your sources in the format (source: X). Never say what can be fetched. If something can be fetched just do so and incorporate it into your output. You must do as thorough an investigation as you can before replying."